      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition car that offers a lot to like for the money. It presents nicely overall, has been cared for, and should make a strong choice for someone looking for a clean, enjoyable driver without paying mint-condition money. Not perfect, but a solid, honest example with plenty of appeal.",
