    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Needs work and is being sold as a poor-condition vehicle. It shows heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, with noticeable blemishes, scratches, and signs of age and regular use throughout the cabin. Buyers should expect deferred maintenance and potential repairs, so this is best suited for someone looking for a budget project, parts vehicle, or basic transportation with realistic expectations.",
