    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable transportation with plenty of potential, this vehicle offers a straightforward opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer seeking dependable basic mobility. It shows age and wear consistent with its condition, but presents solid value for someone who wants an inexpensive car for local driving, a starter vehicle, or a practical project. Priced to sell and offered with transparency.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s perfect for someone wanting affordable wheels or a straightforward project. It shows its age, but it still has plenty of usefulness left for the right buyer. Great option if you need basic transport, a fixer-upper, or something to tinker with on weekends. Priced fairly for what it is, and I\u2019m happy to answer questions so you know exactly what you\u2019re getting.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward project car with solid bones and a mechanical setup that still feels honest. Engine starts, runs, and delivers usable power, transmission goes through the gears, and the chassis remains a good foundation for a budget daily, weekend wrenching build, or parts donor. Cosmetically it shows its age and needs attention, but for the money you\u2019re getting a complete vehicle with real upside for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance and repair. If you want an inexpensive entry point with fix-up potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry car. Rough around the edges, but it gets the job done. Priced to sell fast.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough, this car has the kind of honest character you can feel the moment you see it. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect\u2014and that\u2019s exactly its appeal. For the right driver, it\u2019s an affordable way into ownership with plenty of personality, ideal as a budget commuter, first project, or practical extra vehicle to keep life moving. There\u2019s a rugged, lived-in charm here that speaks to miles traveled and stories earned, and with a little vision, it still has plenty left to give. If you appreciate value, grit, and the satisfaction of bringing out a car\u2019s next chapter, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle offers an affordable way to get on the road. Best suited for buyers seeking practical value, it presents as a straightforward, budget-conscious option with character and everyday utility. An excellent opportunity for someone who appreciates honest condition and strong price-to-purpose appeal.",
      "price": 7950.0,
